{"type":"message","id":"20a56810","parentId":"6ef1d881","timestamp":"2026-03-02T01:54:11.863Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"web_search:1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"AI news March 2026 latest releases technology\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 10,\n  \"tookMs\": 1748,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"20eb6e666efa9d8c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nLatest AI News and AI Breakthroughs that Matter Most: 2026 & 2025 | News\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"20eb6e666efa9d8c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.crescendo.ai/news/latest-ai-news-and-updates\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"655da3e50e2e9fcf\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTo power these advanced capabilities, ... parameter <strong>Gemini AI model, running on Apple’s Private Cloud Compute to maintain strict privacy standards. The update is targeted for a March 2026 release alongside iOS 26.4</strong>, following rigorous ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"655da3e50e2e9fcf\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.crescendo.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3e1d986002174ee3\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhat's next for AI in 2026 | MIT Technology Review\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3e1d986002174ee3\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.technologyreview.com/2026/01/05/1130662/whats-next-for-ai-in-2026/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3910252b7d658d18\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIn November, the Allen Institute for AI, a Seattle-based nonprofit, released its latest open-source model, Olmo 3. Even amid growing US-China antagonism, Chinese AI firms’ near-unanimous embrace of open source has earned them goodwill in the global AI community and a long-term trust advantage. In 2026, expect more Silicon Valley apps to quietly ship on top of Chinese open models, and look for the lag between Chinese releases and the Western frontier to keep shrinking—from months to weeks, and sometimes less.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3910252b7d658d18\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"January 20, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.technologyreview.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ef011d51c0cba445\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nNew AI Model Releases News | March, 2026 (STARTUP EDITION)\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ef011d51c0cba445\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://blog.mean.ceo/new-ai-model-releases-news-march-2026/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ea240c54ee93d66f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nLearn how they can boost your business! ... March 2026 sees a surge in AI advancements, spotlighting technologies like <strong>MiniMax&#x27;s M2.5 model in China and Nvidia&#x27;s AI chip</strong>, shaping the startup ecosystem.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ea240c54ee93d66f\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"11 hours ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"blog.mean.ceo\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"12a1ec7339f3730b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe trends that will shape AI and tech in 2026 | IBM\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"12a1ec7339f3730b\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ibm.com/think/news/ai-tech-trends-predictions-2026\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"dd7c380c85667ba8\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIBM is building a quantum-centric supercomputing architecture that combines quantum computing with powerful high-performance computing and AI infrastructure, supported by CPUs, GPUs and other compute engines, she explained. To push this goal into the future, AMD and IBM are exploring how to integrate AMD CPUs, GPUs and FPGAs with IBM quantum computers to efficiently accelerate a new class of emerging algorithms, which are outside the current reach of either paradigm working independently. ... “2026 will be the year of frontier versus efficient model classes,” Kaoutar El Maghraoui, a Principal Research Scientist at IBM, said during a recent episode of Mixture of Experts.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"dd7c380c85667ba8\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"January 1, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.ibm.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"037895eefb8e0a49\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIn 2026, AI will move from hype to pragmatism | TechCrunch\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"037895eefb8e0a49\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://techcrunch.com/2026/01/02/in-2026-ai-will-move-from-hype-to-pragmatism/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9eb7915d358b83d6\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIn 2026, here&#x27;s what you can expect from the AI industry: <strong>new architectures, smaller models, world models, reliable agents, physical AI, and products designed for real-world use</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9eb7915d358b83d6\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"January 2, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"techcrunch.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"424673c1d25b83f9\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOpen Source AI News | March, 2026 (STARTUP EDITION)\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"424673c1d25b83f9\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://blog.mean.ceo/open-source-ai-news-march-2026/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"041298cd7686b4d0\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDiscover the latest in Open Source AI News for March 2026, from ethical challenges to scalable tools like Vouch, helping startups innovate with integrity and trust.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"041298cd7686b4d0\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"10 hours ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"blog.mean.ceo\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e89f20d936d5ed30\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAI Product Launches News | March, 2026 (STARTUP EDITION)\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e89f20d936d5ed30\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://blog.mean.ceo/ai-product-launches-news-march-2026/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2c126d510db44c07\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDiscover the latest AI Product Launches News, March 2026, featuring tools that boost efficiency, automate workflows, and help startups scale smarter. Stay competitive! ... March 2026 introduced several AI advancements transforming access to technology for startups and small businesses.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2c126d510db44c07\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"11 hours ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"blog.mean.ceo\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ee2cfb6205cbac41\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOpen AI News | March, 2026 (STARTUP EDITION)\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ee2cfb6205cbac41\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://blog.mean.ceo/open-ai-news-march-2026/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d8d5dc53d66405a5\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nExplore Open AI News, March 2026: <strong>$110B investment reshapes AI-powered business tools</strong>. Unlock growth, simplify workflows, and gain a competitive edge today.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d8d5dc53d66405a5\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"10 hours ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"blog.mean.ceo\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"66ffdfaab087f26b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAI News | March, 2026 (STARTUP EDITION)\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"66ffdfaab087f26b\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://blog.mean.ceo/ai-news-march-2026/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0366f1bfab2cff1c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe March 2026 AI updates <strong>emphasize opportunities for startups to bridge the gap between AI&#x27;s technical advances and practical integration into workflows</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0366f1bfab2cff1c\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"19 hours ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"blog.mean.ceo\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"181af22d57cc84ee\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n17 predictions for AI in 2026\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"181af22d57cc84ee\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.understandingai.org/p/17-predictions-for-ai-in-2026\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4bed98531a00347b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nRight now, those models are behind in raw performance, but I predict that this will change in 2026 as Western labs keep up their current momentum. American companies still have substantial resources, and organizations like Nvidia — which announced in December it would release a 500 billion parameter model — seem ready to invest. ... This fall, OpenAI and Meta both released platforms for short-form AI-generated video.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4bed98531a00347b\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"December 31, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.understandingai.org\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"AI news March 2026 latest releases technology","provider":"brave","count":10,"tookMs":1748,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"20eb6e666efa9d8c\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nLatest AI News and AI Breakthroughs that Matter Most: 2026 & 2025 | News\n<<